      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) must be reported for all QoI at each operating point; GCI < 5% required.",
      "rationale": "GCI was computed for all five operating points; pressure head GCI was below 5% but hemolysis index GCI exceeded 5% at two operating points, holding achievedLevel at 3."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/test-conditions-cou2",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
